Paper: hep-th/9504067

Date: 1995-04-12

Title: On the Equivalence of the Maxwell-Chern-Simons Theory and a Self-Dual

ModelAuthors: R. Banerjee, H. J. Rothe and K. D. Rothe

Comments: 6 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D52 (1995) 3750-3752

We study the connection between the Green functions of theMaxwell-Chern-Simons theory and a self-dual model by starting from thephase-space path integral representation of the Deser-Jackiw master Lagrangian.Their equivalence is established modulo time-ordering ambiguities.